It's depressing that the support role also keeps getting worse because the support items are being used by other lanes and abusing them, leading to the item being nerfed. (Ex: {{item:3092}} )

FeelsBadMan

{{sticker:zombie-nunu-bummed}}

You're a fool if you think supports have to have exhaust...

There are exactly three junglers who have good objective control without smite: {{champion:20}} {{champion:31}} {{champion:2}} 
And Cho'Gath needs the support to follow him for the first rotation otherwise he gets ridiculously under-leveled.

There are by contrast a large number of supports who can run without exhaust: {{champion:89}} {{champion:117}} {{champion:111}} {{champion:9}} {{champion:44}} {{champion:267}} {{champion:61}} {{champion:26}} {{champion:143}} {{champion:412}} {{champion:223}} {{champion:113}} {{champion:80}} {{champion:33}} {{champion:31}} {{champion:64}}

